      "date": "2018-11-27 21:27:03.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPassed optional test review-ldiskfs-arm on CentOS 7.0/x86_64, CentOS 7.0/aarch64 uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-79vm19: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e90b3a31-b57d-47ea-9d7c-0d92cac15d44 ran 4 tests.",
